# ── Credentials & secrets ────────────────────────────────────────────────────
**/secrets.yaml
**/*_token*
**/*.env
CREDENTIALS.local.yaml

# ── AI / agent context (local-only, never public) ────────────────────────────
CLAUDE.md
.cursor/

# ── Internal planning & orchestration artifacts ───────────────────────────────
# These contain personal URLs, NAS paths, internal state, or are stale QA logs
# not useful to a new installer.
DEVELOPMENT_REPORT.md
IMPLEMENTATION_READY.md
REVISED_PLAN_SUMMARY.md
QA_REPORT_CONSOLIDATED.md
SECRETS_CHECKLIST.md

# ── NAS-specific deploy tool ──────────────────────────────────────────────────
# Hardcodes /home/dev/nas/Volume1/... paths; not portable to other installs.
tools/

# ── Internal task plans & workflow ───────────────────────────────────────────
# Instance-specific: personal URLs, NAS paths, stale prerequisite state.
_management/tasks/
_management/WORKFLOW.md

# ── Python cache ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
__pycache__/
*.pyc
*.pyo

# ── OS noise ─────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
.DS_Store
Thumbs.db
